HEADWORD: Water mill
<hw>Wa"ter mill`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A mill whose machinery is moved
by water; -- distinguished from a <contr>windmill</contr>, and a
<contr>steam mill</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water mint</ent>⟦br⟧
